list.name: Default
list.comment: Fixed some bugs in the Maven configuration files.

task.summary: Default task
Improved the feature maps implementations.
Moved the configuration files of each module to their corresponding resources directories.
Made some small changes to the general project settings.
Switched to using the GICS ID as the primary key for the sectors, the industry groups, the industries, and the sub-industries.
Added support for importing the GICS data and fixed a minor bug (the sub-industries description field was not included in the corresponding builder).
Switched to using batch inserts for importing the GICS data.
Created a new library with data structures.
Transformed the binary logistic regression classifiers to use data sets instead of lists of data instances and fixed several bugs.
Made several changes to the data library.
Simplified the data library.
Added support for serializing boolean variables.
Fixed a bug related to the sparse vectors serialization method.
Added some more unit tests for the SparseVector class to allow catching bugs related to serialization, similar to those fixed with the previous commit.
Changed the serialization method for all the classifiers.
Added multi-view data instances support in the data library.
Added support for prepending and appending vectors with values.
Added support for a dotPlusConstant() operation in the vector classes.
Added support for the saxpyPlusConstant() operation in some of the vector classes.
Added support for a bias term in the binary logistic regression implementations.
Removed the trade module from this project.
Replaced usages of sun.reflect.generics.reflectiveObjects.NotImplementedException with java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException.
Added support for multi-view data sets.
Converted the integrator class to use data sets instead of lists of data instances.
Made a minor improvement on the classifiers serialization method.
Fixed some unit tests.
Made some minor renaming changes.
Improved the MariaDB feature map so that it uses a properties file for its configuration.
Added support to set the seed in random number generator of the StatisticsUtilities class.
Integrated Bill's changes to the library.
Fixed a bug related to setting values of elements in a sparse vector.
Made the DataSetInMemory continuous random batch iterator changes to all the data set classes and fixed a minor bug in the remove() method of the iterator.
Made some minor changes and additions.
Made the integrator work with data sets instead of lists holding data instances.
Fixed a bug with the saxpyPlusConstant vector operation that resulted in the logistic regression bias term always being equal to zero.
Made some minor changes.
Added support for using an additional custom convergence criterion in the optimization library.
Added support for using an additional custom convergence criterion in the binary logistic regression classifiers.
Added support for robust co-training using our error rates estimation method in the integrator.
Minor re-organization.
Made some minor changes.
Added support for cross-validation based tuning or evaluation data set based tuning on the classification library.
Reverted Bill's previous changes.
Cleaned up the code from some debugging statements.
Switched to using double-valued labels in the logistic regression classifier (for now), in order for Bill to be able to implement his EM-based algorithm.
Minor bug fix related to selecting entries from the database holding the feature maps.
Minor performance improvement.
Made some temporary changes to be able to run for the first time my integrator experiments.
Fixed some bugs in the Maven configuration files.
Fixed some bugs in the Maven configuration files.
